---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Narrows — Analysis"
  description="Scenario analysis and applied research from Narrows. Every figure is a model output. Every assumption is stated."
>

<style>
.page-hero {
  padding: 128px var(--s4) var(--s5);
  max-width: var(--max-w);
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.analysis-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--s3); }
.analysis-item {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: var(--s4);
  align-items: start;
  background: var(--white);
  border: var(--rule-light);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: var(--s3) var(--s4);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: transform 0.2s var(--ease), box-shadow 0.2s;
}
.analysis-item:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(10,37,64,0.07); }
.analysis-item-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.analysis-item-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.analysis-item-body { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 300; }
.analysis-item-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 10px; }
.analysis-item-arrow { font-size: 20px; color: var(--text-tertiary); align-self: center; }
@media (max-width: 600px) { .analysis-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .analysis-item-arrow { display: none; } }
</style>

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">Analysis</div>
  <h1 class="section-title">The model applied to live chokepoint events.</h1>
  <p class="section-lead">Every figure is a model output. Every assumption is stated and substitutable. If you disagree with an input, that is a one-parameter change.</p>

  <div class="analysis-list">
    <a href="/analysis/kra-land-bridge" class="analysis-item">
      <div>
        <div class="analysis-item-tag">Malacca Strait · May 2026</div>
        <div class="analysis-item-title">The Kra Land Bridge: A $31B Question With a $1.4M Answer</div>
        <p class="analysis-item-body">Thailand is fast-tracking a land bridge across the Kra Isthmus. The project is real. The geopolitical logic is real. The commercial case for iron ore and crude is not. The Narrows model runs the numbers.</p>
        <div class="analysis-item-meta">Iron ore · Crude petroleum · Capesize · VLCC · Japan · South Korea · China</div>
      </div>
      <div class="analysis-item-arrow">→</div>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>
